Class CommConfigImpl

java.lang.Object
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.BaseObjectImpl
us.mn.state.dot.tms.server.CommConfigImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
SonarObject, CommConfig, Storable
public class CommConfigImpl extends BaseObjectImpl implements CommConfig
A CommConfig represents a configuration which can be used for one or more CommLinks.

Douglas Lau
